    <p><span>A dependable mentor figure to the protagonists.</span>
      </p></div><div><p><a title="Companies > Nihon Falcom [737 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/nihon-falcom">Falcom</a> has released the third character trailer for <em><a title="Games > Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter [11 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter">Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter</a></em>, introducing Scherazard Harvey. <span id="more-975057"></span></p><p>Here is her official description:</p><blockquote><p>A dependable mentor figure to the protagonists.</p><p>A Senior Bracer known by the name of “Silver Flash.” Possesses a powerful and well-trained physique with an alluring beauty.</p><p>A former apprentice of Estelle’s father, Cassius, and serves as a big sister figure to Estelle and the others. Has a caring and protective personality, but is also known for her love of alcohol and she tends to get a bit too clingy when drunk.</p><p>As a mentor, she keeps an eye on Estelle and the others, offering them support and guidance as they grow.</p></blockquote><!-- AD: content -->
        <p><em>Trails in the Sky 1st Chapter</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [9,778 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a>, <a title="Platforms > Switch [17,261 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/nintendo/switch">Switch</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [23,544 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/3375780/Trails_in_the_Sky_1st_Chapter/" target="_blank">Steam</a> on September 19 worldwide. Read more about the game <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/03/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-main-characters-voice-cast">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/05/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-rolent-characters-and-places-battle-system">here</a>, <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-bose-characters-and-places-location-trailers">here</a>, and <a href="https://www.gematsu.com/2025/06/trails-in-the-sky-1st-chapter-details-tactical-orbments">here</a>.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Character Trailer: Scherazard Harvey</span></h2><p><strong>Japanese</strong></p><p><iframe title="【シェラザード】キャラクタームービー #空の軌跡the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Ukdfvxz8UE8?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Korean</strong></p><p><iframe title="【셰라자드】 캐릭터 무비 #하늘의궤적 #the1st" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/JOGIVxLWWzk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p><p><strong>Traditional Chinese</strong></p><p><iframe title="【雪拉紮德】 角色影片 #空之軌跡the1st" width="500" 